title: Kingdom Rush 1.1.13 Flaandalone w/Premium Content
description:
Kingdom Rush 1.13 (Premium Version)

Hard difficulty is available on this copy, unlike on http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7971610/Kingdom_Rush_1.12_%28Premium_Version%29

Other than that it seems the same as 1.12. I imagine there were bug fixes.

This one has the HEROES and 3 new levels!

About: Defend your kingdom against hordes of orcs, trolls, evil wizards and other nasty fiends in this medieval fantasy fun action packed tower defense game with RTS elements by Ironhide Game Studio. Armed with a mighty arsenal of warriors, mages, archers and crazy dwarves, there is no end to the many strategies available at your disposal!

Official Site: http://www.kingdomrush.com/
